                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108755-2616b612b786?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=100&q=80" class="rounded-circle me-3" width="50" height="50" alt="Photo de profil de Marie Dubois, cliente satisfaite">
                            <div>
                                <h6 class="mb-0">Marie Dubois</h6>
                                <small class="text-muted">Cliente depuis 2021</small>
